  ('medical-tech-moex-04188', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-483fb9c7', 'sub-medical-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '要區分甲狀腺功能低下（hypothyroidism）的三個成因，可注射甲狀腺促素釋素（thyrotropin-releasing hormone, TRH）後，於 0、20、60 分鐘檢測甲狀腺促素（thyroid-stimulating hormone, TSH）濃度。下列何種 患者檢測結果 TSH 不會顯著上升或下降？', '["原發性甲狀腺功能低下（primary hypothyroidism）", "腦下垂體性甲狀腺功能低下（pituitary hypothyroidism）", "下視丘性甲狀腺功能低下（hypothalamic hypothyroidism）", "甲狀腺功能正常者（normal）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "fc9d7636f106", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2c6ed9415169", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111100", "c": "308", "s": "55", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生物化學與臨床生化學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、111年專技...", "original_question_number": 65, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
